profile: Centurion painting is a central Alberta painting company specializing in interior and exterior repaints of all sizes and types. our crew boasts over 20 years of industry experience in the field with past work including everything from stucco repaints to full interior new builds and cabinets. so whether your a project manager looking for a subcontractor for a new hotel or a homeowner that wants a bathroom painted we will make sure the job is done properly and to the highest of standards.
warranty_terms: 3 year warranty for all projects in which we have provided the product or the client provides an approved product and in which the prep work has been done by our crew. Some exclusions may apply.
